                "type": "list[group-id]",
                "constraint": "all[min 1]",
                "quality": null,
                "default": null,
                "conformance": "M",
                "summary": "The GroupList field SHALL contain either the group IDs of all the groups in the Group Table for which the server endpoint is a member of the group (in the case where the GroupList field of the received GetGroupMembership command was empty), or the group IDs of all the groups in the Group Table for which the server endpoint is a member of the group and for which the group ID was included in the the GroupList field of the received GetGroupMembership command (in the case where the GroupList field of the received GetGroupMembership command was not empty). Zigbee: If the total number of groups will cause the maximum payload length of a frame to be exceeded, then the GroupList field SHALL contain only as many groups as will fit."
              }
            ],
